# ERA Finance — Cursor

Long-form project rules were moved to **`.cursor/rules/*.mdc`** (Project Rules). Do not duplicate them here.

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `.cursor/rules/erafinance-local-dev.mdc` | Env, Docker, Prisma migrations, i18n, dev commands |
| `.cursor/rules/erafinance-module-map.mdc` | Module names ↔ `apps/api` / `apps/web` / Prisma |
| `.cursor/rules/erafinance-agent-roles.mdc` | Agent personas, security, tenancy, compliance |
| `.cursor/rules/erafinance-ui-design.mdc` | Web UI: follow root `DESIGN.md` when editing `apps/web` |

Attach `@PRD.md`, `@TZ.md` when product/spec matter (they are in `.cursorignore`). `DESIGN.md` is indexed; `@DESIGN.md` works for extra emphasis.
